&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Looking for a candidate to help provide a high level of patient hotel services on our Private Patient Suite. Responsible for the daily cleaning of our Private Patients room and the Ward itself. Will need to be able to keep to the demands of the ward and the high turn over of rooms daily. Must be friendly of nature. Previous experience desired but not necessary. Knowledge of COSHH and RIDDOR advantageous but not essential. An ability to use a computer may be necessary to keep up to date with training requirements. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
